./.title: Introduction
./.body:
Rally Report - Italy
This report is unofficial and is not associated in any way with the Fédération Internationale de l’Automobile (FIA) or WRC Promoter GmbH.
Rally Italia Sardegna (2018-06-07 to 2018-06-10) runs over 20 competitive special stages. The distance covered on the special stages is 314.36km, with an overall rally distance of 1388.03km. The special stage surface type is predominantly Gravel.
